The paper discusses a wireless power transfer technology and its optimization using a feedback system and analytical models. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) as well as electromagnetic theory (cs.EM). The use of a feedback system and control also suggests the involvement of systems and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of dc-dc conversion circuits, which falls under the domain of electronic engineering (cs.ET) and power engineering (cs.PE).
